    autocmd BufLeave \[BufExplorer\] nmap ds <Plug>Dsurround
    autocmd BufEnter \[BufExplorer\] nunmap drw
    autocmd BufLeave \[BufExplorer\] nnoremap drw
                \ :<C-U>call DeleteRubbishWhitespace()<CR>
augroup END

